Name: adult spinal cord ependymoma
Definition: A breast sarcoma that arises from bone.

Name: obsolete recurrent uterine sarcoma
Definition: A uterine Corpus sarcoma that has recurred after it has been treated.

Name: obsolete transitional cell carcinoma of the ureter with glandular differentiation
Definition: A uterine Corpus sarcoma that has recurred after it has been treated.
